"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"0c0f62c1-1789-419c-ba07-e816956394e8","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Avant de toucher à quoi que ce soit, intégrez ces trois principes :","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"5e45dfaa-7662-4708-92b7-9a15e498f85a","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"La règle des 15 minutes :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Ne travaillez jamais plus de 15 minutes d''affilée sans une pause de 5 minutes. Utilisez un minuteur.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"b6b70560-6e95-41f9-902f-a53fe37f0ada","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Pas de tri émotionnel au début :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Si vous hésitez plus de 3 secondes sur un objet, posez-le. On ne traite que l''évident pour commencer.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"3e61d2a1-0ca5-4deb-9332-7df62309c1f8","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Le casque sur les oreilles :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Écoutez un podcast ou de la musique. Cela \\"occupe\\" la partie anxieuse de votre cerveau pendant que vos mains travaillent.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"688a350f-b298-40a7-b827-ab804eaa265d","type":"divider","props":{},"children":[]},{"id":"05775931-1e24-4383-83cc-c2e584191213","type":"heading","props":{"level":2,"textColor":"default","isToggleable":false,"textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"2. Phase 1 : Le \\"Trash Bag Walk\\" (Jours 1 à 3)","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"28ab1d41-5328-412c-9fac-3a1e933665de","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"L''objectif est de libérer de l''espace visuel sans réfléchir.","type":"text","styles":{"italic":true}}],"children":[]},{"id":"e4891b76-97c6-46d9-918b-6b80c6c138e8","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Jour 1 : Les déchets évidents.","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Prenez un grand sac poubelle. Parcourez l''appartement et ne ramassez ","type":"text","styles":{}},{"text":"que","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" ce qui est indiscutablement un déchet (emballages vides, prospectus, restes de nourriture, bouteilles vides). Ne rangez rien, ne nettoyez rien. Juste le sac.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"51095710-9868-4150-84a1-38801b2d49e4","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Jour 2 : Le linge sale.","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Rassemblez tout le linge qui traîne en un seul point (une montagne au milieu d''une pièce ou dans des paniers). Si vous avez une machine, lancez-en une seule. Ne la pliez pas encore, l''important est de libérer les surfaces.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"14a0f48d-8f89-4fec-8e54-5e4c0fd18894","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Jour 3 : La vaisselle et les surfaces planes.","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Rassemblez toute la vaisselle sale dans l''évier (ou à côté). Dégagez simplement les tables et le plan de travail de la cuisine pour pouvoir \\"respirer\\".","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"bc6580cc-d515-4ace-9e8c-afa424fe8d69","type":"divider","props":{},"children":[]},{"id":"b598ad54-a291-4706-af86-aec48b8cb89b","type":"heading","props":{"level":2,"textColor":"default","isToggleable":false,"textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"3. Phase 2 : Le Tri par Zones (Jours 4 à 10)","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"c431795f-b863-4982-a4d4-4e1004050e5c","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"On ne regarde plus l''appartement entier, seulement un petit carré à la fois.","type":"text","styles":{"italic":true}}],"children":[]},{"id":"c0a748ce-58ef-478b-a04d-695e61b48f40","type":"heading","props":{"level":3,"textColor":"default","isToggleable":false,"textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"La Méthode des 3 Bacs","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"7eb1c456-490c-4edd-85f1-a82eba883af9","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Dans chaque zone, travaillez avec trois contenants :","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"cad6243c-23da-49ee-be24-334e0dfccf68","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"À jeter","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" (sac poubelle).","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"2d72f49d-418d-49ed-8bce-1e87e9648e43","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"À donner/vendre","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" (carton).","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"b50ec127-c3c3-4423-a6f3-0587aadba551","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Pas à sa place","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" (une caisse pour ce qui appartient à une autre pièce).","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"407cea9a-63f7-470a-889c-44c15a364c7e","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Jours 4-5 : La Salle de Bain & WC.","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" C''est souvent la plus petite pièce, le succès y est rapide. Jetez les produits périmés ou vides. Nettoyez le miroir (effet psychologique immédiat).","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"23271221-9c80-4357-8628-84f79dd62f2c","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Jours 6-8 : La Chambre.","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Priorité au lit. Changez les draps. Dégagez le sol autour du lit pour pouvoir circuler sans enjamber d''objets.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"675ae4f2-887a-41a0-8995-298a2c80ba16","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Jours 9-10 : Le Salon.","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Attaquez-vous à une seule étagère ou un seul coin par session de 15 minutes. Si une pile de papiers vous effraie, mettez-la dans une boîte \\"À traiter plus tard\\" pour ne pas bloquer votre élan.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"9544ccaf-0352-470d-ac1b-e7ab74cd6191","type":"divider","props":{},"children":[]},{"id":"836dd7fa-0d69-4464-8105-610f5cb43160","type":"heading","props":{"level":2,"textColor":"default","isToggleable":false,"textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"4. Phase 3 : Le Grand Nettoyage (Jours 11 à 14)","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"583710b0-0404-4af4-bcb2-8e5cae6a828b","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Maintenant que les objets sont triés, on s''occupe de la saleté.","type":"text","styles":{"italic":true}}],"children":[]},{"id":"afc1b07d-0028-48a2-8d57-5517f756d41b","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Jour 11 : Dégraissage.","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Cuisine et plaques de cuisson. Utilisez des produits qui agissent seuls (laissez poser le produit 10 min avant d''essuyer).","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"43dd18b6-9e9c-4680-b120-22fa7e40b0b5","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Jour 12 : Poussière et Vitres.","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Faites le tour de l''appartement avec un chiffon humide.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"4286e6f9-fbfd-4376-9f75-b64262c496c5","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Jour 13 : Le Sol.","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Passez l''aspirateur partout, puis la serpillière. C''est l''étape qui transforme l''appartement de \\"rangé\\" à \\"propre\\".","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"004d201d-2e8b-487c-beac-086af2f20237","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Jour 14 : Finitions et Célébration.","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Sortez les derniers sacs, portez les dons à une association. Achetez une plante ou une bougie parfumée pour marquer le renouveau.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"7defb7f8-9db4-4f7b-810b-e4eb493484eb","type":"divider","props":{},"children":[]},{"id":"9fee11c8-4197-4929-9b7a-830ac5541582","type":"heading","props":{"level":2,"textColor":"default","isToggleable":false,"textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Le kit de survie immédiat","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"ba4cc4d8-4384-473d-b5b4-de1ad98fba86","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Pour commencer demain matin sans stress, vous n''avez besoin que de ceci :","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"4ad5ec74-8712-49be-95f3-7adf47130144","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Un rouleau de sacs poubelle de 50L (solides).","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"202bc763-31c4-421b-a145-49af2431b90d","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Une paire de gants ménagers (pour se sentir \\"protégé\\" de la saleté).","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"f675a269-e908-4785-b1ad-571f6d1f2132","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Une playlist ou un podcast que vous adorez.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"d15b27cc-1999-41a7-9fc1-7f69b2320d6c","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"L''astuce d''expert :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Ne cherchez pas la perfection. Un appartement \\"mieux qu''hier\\" est déjà une victoire totale. Si vous ne faites que 15 minutes aujourd''hui, vous avez déjà gagné contre l''inertie.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"bbb969fa-5a30-456b-86c0-d8709f7b16af","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Souhaitez-vous que nous détaillions ensemble la liste de courses pour les produits de nettoyage essentiels (et pas chers) afin de vous éviter de réfléchir dans le rayon du magasin ?","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"7c8fbe0a-c563-4b58-9c3d-215633327ed0","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[],"children":[]},{"id":"872c6309-8808-4b04-83ef-fa9dfffd876d","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[],"children":[]}]', '{"appState":{"viewBackgroundColor":"#ffffff"},"elements":[]}', '{}', 'text', '1', '[]'), ('146', 'z1kjc80h', 'Achats', '0', '2025-12-29 22:20:58.844404+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:02.032356+00', 'text', '[{"id":"5156579b-6fe8-4748-a500-12b4b8ec2f2d","type":"heading","props":{"level":2,"textColor":"default","isToggleable":false,"textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Achats","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"34ad6e5a-e15c-44ae-ade2-a882843c7736","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"C''est une excellente stratégie. Moins de flacons sous l''évier signifie moins de fouillis visuel et moins de questions à se poser. On va se concentrer sur ","type":"text","styles":{}},{"text":"le strict nécessaire","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" qui permet de tout nettoyer, du sol au plafond, avec seulement 4 produits et 3 accessoires.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"6531e7b3-2381-4ab9-80c6-aff42c932be9","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Voici votre liste de courses \\"Impact Maximum / Charge Minimale\\" :","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"a45c8809-f309-46a8-875a-8d5902d97f95","type":"heading","props":{"level":3,"textColor":"default","isToggleable":false,"textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Les 4 Produits (Le \\"Kit Liquide\\")","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"387fbec5-0d2a-4bb9-8661-7ad329eb5f96","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Le Vinaigre Blanc (1,5L ou 5L) :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" C''est votre produit miracle. Il détartre (robinets, douche), nettoie les vitres et désinfecte légèrement. C''est le moins cher du rayon.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"8805601f-93f1-4b31-99ce-609e75ed1a30","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Le Liquide Vaisselle :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Ne sert pas qu''à la vaisselle. C''est le meilleur dégraissant pour la cuisine (plaques, plan de travail) et, mélangé à de l''eau chaude, c''est parfait pour nettoyer les sols.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"bc3e8876-3d33-419a-b238-ee042d2c2bd0","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Un Spray Multi-surfaces Désinfectant :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Prenez-en un seul (souvent étiqueté \\"Sanytol\\" ou marque distributeur). Utilisez-le pour les zones \\"sensibles\\" : lunette des WC, poignées de porte, et le frigo. L''odeur de \\"propre\\" aide aussi beaucoup au moral.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"654dbc3b-705e-4bdb-b853-4b797ea012e3","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Un Gel WC :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Pour laisser agir au fond de la cuvette pendant que vous faites autre chose.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"1288e8d0-db24-4c6f-9929-021a3c572c4e","type":"heading","props":{"level":3,"textColor":"default","isToggleable":false,"textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Les 3 Accessoires (Le \\"Kit Action\\")","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"6887e7fa-2f71-476f-a6b9-33dd44ebeb56","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Sacs Poubelle 50L (Ultra-résistants) :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Prenez la qualité supérieure avec poignées coulissantes. Rien n''est plus décourageant qu''un sac qui craque au milieu du salon.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"55b015d6-ee32-43ef-a983-f4793b8b24fe","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Un lot de 5 Chiffons Microfibres :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Ils sont bien plus efficaces que les éponges classiques. Vous pouvez en dédier un à chaque pièce (ex: le bleu pour la salle de bain, le jaune pour la cuisine). Ils se lavent en machine.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"868cc663-7359-41a6-a818-702f850e820a","type":"numberedListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Un lot d''Éponges (avec côté grattant) :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Pour les taches tenaces dans l''évier ou la douche.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"68e68585-3c08-4d17-86f4-9b826c31511d","type":"divider","props":{},"children":[]},{"id":"6d76389a-150e-4752-8b7b-45b3c78f7cab","type":"heading","props":{"level":3,"textColor":"default","isToggleable":false,"textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Comment les utiliser sans réfléchir ?","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"ee9b3f64-db74-4f20-8f54-8002144e4d73","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Pour tout ce qui brille (vitres, miroirs, robinets) :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Vinaigre blanc + un chiffon microfibre sec.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"4aff5a07-d80b-46e7-93cd-5cc711ee9115","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Pour tout ce qui est gras (cuisine, tables) :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Une goutte de liquide vaisselle sur une éponge humide.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"09ac7743-7e26-4346-a975-a6897190097b","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Pour tout ce qui doit être \\"sain\\" (WC, poignées) :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Le spray désinfectant + un chiffon.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"6c833549-5864-4612-9209-a1df05787d53","type":"bulletListItem","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Pour le sol :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Un seau d''eau chaude + un bouchon de liquide vaisselle. Simple et efficace.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"7fd3a3fd-c93d-4cd0-9f5c-9d6ebc2bf862","type":"quote","props":{"textColor":"default","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Conseil de pro :","type":"text","styles":{"bold":true}},{"text":" Ne cherchez pas à transvaser les produits dans des jolis flacons ou à faire des mélanges compliqués. Gardez les bouteilles d''origine, posez-les dans un petit panier ou un seau, et déplacez ce seau avec vous de pièce en pièce.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"b52e8572-2461-4b9f-93f6-66e546a35aa4","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"Est-ce que vous avez déjà un balai et une pelle, ou est-ce que je dois les ajouter à la liste des indispensables ?","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"9631e6ee-6f6f-4902-a338-be160290abd4","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[],"children":[]}]', '{"appState":{"viewBackgroundColor":"#ffffff"},"elements":[]}', '{}', 'text', '3', '[]'), ('148', '5sqfv356', 'Untitled', '0', '2025-12-29 23:39:07.678194+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:02.032356+00', 'text', '[]', '{}', '{}', 'text', '1', '[]'), ('149', 'slq95eal', 'Untitled', '0', '2025-12-29 23:39:08.37281+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:02.032356+00', 'text', '[]', '{}', '{}', 'text', '1', '[]'), ('150', '4d7bc29q', 'Untitled', '0', '2025-12-29 23:39:10.395294+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:02.032356+00', 'text', '[]', '{}', '{}', 'text', '1', '[]'), ('151', 'xg7sa42l', 'Untitled', '0', '2025-12-29 23:39:12.159562+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:02.032356+00', 'text', '[]', '{}', '{}', 'text', '1', '[]'), ('152', 'vt0em975', 'Untitled', '0', '2025-12-29 23:39:15.187956+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:02.032356+00', 'text', '[]', '{"appState":{"viewBackgroundColor":"#ffffff"},"elements":[]}', '{}', 'text', '1', '[]'), ('153', '3ajq36bd', 'Untitled', '0', '2025-12-29 23:39:18.797579+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:02.032356+00', 'text', '[]', '{}', '{}', 'text', '1', '[]'), ('154', 'wcmcww6n', 'Untitled', '0', '2025-12-29 23:39:27.034946+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:02.032356+00', 'text', '[]', '{}', '{}', 'text', '1', '[]'), ('155', '584b40vd', 'Untitled', '0', '2025-12-30 00:42:39.624365+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:02.032356+00', 'text', '[]', '{"appState":{"viewBackgroundColor":"#ffffff"},"elements":[]}', '{}', 'text', '1', '[]'), ('156', '77ekwvs4', 'Untitled', '0', '2025-12-30 00:46:04.179551+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:02.032356+00', 'text', '[]', '{"appState":{"viewBackgroundColor":"#ffffff"},"elements":[]}', '{}', 'text', '1', '[]'), ('157', 'y8qa6pg8', 'La Vie En Rose Cafe', '0', '2025-12-30 11:02:16.464134+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:02.032356+00', 'text', '[{"id":"719d5fd5-5ecd-4d25-83ea-25770b437f76","type":"heading","props":{"level":2,"textColor":"default","isToggleable":false,"textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"La Vie En Rose Cafe","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"195da4f4-5dd4-45bb-b9d1-e6529e24f0a1","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[{"text":"EazyDiner is all about finding cafes and restaurants that have a homely, laid-back vibe and are simple enough to just walk in and enjoy. This Hyderabad cafe fits the bill perfectly. The European menu is a delight and is curated with great thought, the restaurant looks really nice from the inside. ","type":"text","styles":{}},{"href":"https://www.eazydiner.com/hyderabad/la-vie-en-rose-cafe-gachibowli-hyderabad-701439","type":"link","content":[{"text":"La Vie En Rose Cafe","type":"text","styles":{}}]},{"text":", through its taste and mood, among other things, slowly makes its presence felt. It is a great place to relax, talk to friends, and have a meal that is fulfilling and not rushed.","type":"text","styles":{}}],"children":[]},{"id":"c265619c-fa3c-4697-9776-29562ce889cb","type":"paragraph","props":{"textColor":"default","textAlignment":"left","backgroundColor":"default"},"content":[],"children":[]}]', '{"appState":{"viewBackgroundColor":"#ffffff"},"elements":[{"x":189,"y":209,"id":"Wl265oZ2VsyQu3ufIe3-Q","link":null,"seed":911080865,"text":"","type":"text","angle":0,"index":"a0","width":8,"height":25,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"opacity":100,"updated":1767092609878,"version":3,"fontSize":20,"groupIds":[],"fillStyle":"solid","isDeleted":true,"roughness":1,"roundness":null,"textAlign":"left","autoResize":true,"fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"containerId":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","strokeStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"originalText":"","versionNonce":1945367873,"boundElements":null,"verticalAlign":"top","backgroundColor":"transparent"},{"x":217,"y":81,"id":"SpbdaxfrSxwAIIpK_5JeX","link":null,"seed":2086033665,"text":"","type":"text","angle":0,"index":"a1","width":8,"height":25,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"opacity":100,"updated":1767092614997,"version":3,"fontSize":20,"groupIds":[],"fillStyle":"solid","isDeleted":true,"roughness":1,"roundness":null,"textAlign":"left","autoResize":true,"fontFamily":5,"l