ve a homely, laid-back vibe and\\nare simple enough to just walk in\\nand enjoy. This Hyderabad cafe\\nfits the bill perfectly. The\\nEuropean menu is a delight and\\nis curated with great thought,\\nthe restaurant looks really nice\\nfrom the inside. [La Vie En Rose\\nCafe]\\n(https://www.eazydiner.com/hyd\\nerabad/la-vie-en-rose-cafe-\\ngachibowli-hyderabad-701439),\\nthrough its taste and mood,\\namong other things, slowly\\nmakes its presence felt. It is a\\ngreat place to relax, talk to\\nfriends, and have a meal that is\\nfulfilling and not rushed.","type":"text","angle":0,"index":"a3","width":319.1397705078125,"height":500,"locked":false,"frameId":null,"opacity":100,"updated":1767092638883,"version":42,"fontSize":20,"groupIds":[],"fillStyle":"solid","isDeleted":true,"roughness":1,"roundness":null,"textAlign":"left","autoResize":false,"fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"containerId":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","strokeStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"originalText":"EazyDiner is all about finding cafes and restaurants that have a homely, laid-back vibe and are simple enough to just walk in and enjoy. This Hyderabad cafe fits the bill perfectly. The European menu is a delight and is curated with great thought, the restaurant looks really nice from the inside. [La Vie En Rose Cafe](https://www.eazydiner.com/hyderabad/la-vie-en-rose-cafe-gachibowli-hyderabad-701439), through its taste and mood, among other things, slowly makes its presence felt. It is a great place to relax, talk to friends, and have a meal that is fulfilling and not rushed.","versionNonce":819740303,"boundElements":null,"verticalAlign":"top","backgroundColor":"transparent"}]}', '{}', 'text', '2', '[]'), ('268', 'y8qa6pg8', 'drawing-2', '0', '2025-12-30 11:04:09.879936+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:02.032356+00', 'drawing', '[]', '{"appState":{"viewBackgroundColor":"#ffffff"},"elements":[]}', '{}', 'text', '4', '[]'), ('269', 'c1nz27z4', 'drawing-1', '0', '2025-12-27 02:11:25.338415+00', '2026-01-15 05:53:0